      "moduleShortLabel": "Modules 1-4",
      "questionNumber": 50,
      "type": "single",
      "promptHtml": "<p><strong>A technician is configuring a new Cisco 2960 switch. What is the effect of issuing the BranchSw(config-if)# mdix auto command?</strong></p>",
      "promptText": "A technician is configuring a new Cisco 2960 switch. What is the effect of issuing the BranchSw(config-if)# mdix auto command?",
