      "questionNumber": 42,
      "type": "single",
      "promptHtml": "<p><strong>What characteristic completes the following statement?<br />\nWhen an IPv6 static route is configured, as a backup route to a static route in the routing table, the &#8220;distance&#8221; command is used with &#8230;&#8230;</strong></p>",
