      "promptHtml": "<p><strong>Refer to the exhibit. Which type of IPv6 static route is configured in the exhibit?</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"assets/exhibits/ccna2-m14-16/q045-1-3607cf3d42.gif\" alt=\"\" /></p>",
