      "moduleShortLabel": "CCNA1 Final",
      "questionNumber": 40,
      "type": "single",
      "promptHtml": "<p><strong>Refer to the exhibit. A user issues the command netstat –r on a workstation. Which IPv6 address is one of the link-local addresses of the workstation?</strong><br />\n<img src=\"assets/exhibits/ccna1-final-practice/q040-1-f750905d73.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>",
